quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  3,53,"Our Lord, we believe in what You have sent down and [thus] have followed the Messenger, so enroll us among the witnesses"
  3,54,"They plotted, while God plotted; however God is the best Plotter"
  3,55,"So God said: \"Jesus, I shall gather you up and lift you towards Me and purify you from those who disbelieve, and place those who follow you ahead of those who disbelieve until Resurrection Day. Then to Me will be your return, and I shall decide among you (all) concerning anything you have been disagreeing about"
  3,56,"As for those who disbelieve, I will punish them severely in this world and the Hereafter. They will have no supporters"
  3,57,"As for those who believe and perform honorable deeds, He will repay them their earnings. God does not love wrongdoers"
  3,58,That which We recite to you comes from the signs and the wise Reminder
  3,59,"Jesus´ case with God was the same as Adam´s: He created him from dust; then told him: ´Be!\" and he was"
  3,60,"Truth comes from your Lord, so do not be a waverer"
  3,61,"Tell anyone who argues with you concerning it, once knowledge has come to you; \"Come, let us call our children and your children, our women and your women, ourselves and yourselves together; then let us plead, and place God´s curse upon the liars"